---
title: Onion Chutney-Glazed Chicken with Roasted Veggies & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: An onion chutney is truly an all-rounder. It can go with anything, so why not try it with golden seared chicken? It’s going to blow your mind with the sweet and sticky tastes on top of a roast veggie toss. It’s another win for onion chutney!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
